| History                 = '''Donahue Development''' was an [[United States of America|american]] Research & Development company owned and directed by businessman [[Trevor Donahue (Earth-616)|Trevor Donahue]].{{r|Iron Man Vol 3 29}}

When Trevor Donahue decided to give former rival [[Anthony Stark (Earth-616)|Tony Stark]] full control of Donahue Development's assets and facilities, Stark rebranded the company '''Stark Enterprises''', setting its headquarters in the former Donahue Development's [[New York City]] [[Donahue Development Building (New York)|building]].{{r|Iron Man Vol 3 45}}

